      "_value": "Let's go see #p100# in #m10000000# again."
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I ran into #p100# the fisherman again in #m10000000#. This time, he wanted to get his wife #t4031043#s for her birthday. He asked me to get #b20 #t4031043#s#k for him. The scent of #t4031043# last over 500 years... and according to #p100#, they can be found in the #p609# again, where the flower may be found. Man... do I HAVE to go in there again??"
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I got #p100# all #b20 #t4031043#s#k. They have a nice scent, but 20 of them? Makes my head spin... As a sign of appreciation, #p100# gave me a nice glove he found inside the ship. I mean, it looks like someone accidentally left that glove in there... is he allowed to give it to me like that? What if I wear this around town and run into its actual owner??"
    },
    "demandSummary": {
      "_dirName": "demandSummary",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "#i4031043# #t4031043# #b#c4031043# / 20"
    }
