  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Ohhhh, you're the one that helped me out the other day. You look much stronger now. How's traveling these days? I actually have another favor to ask you... this time, my wife's birthday is coming up and I need more flowers. Can you get them for me?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Thank you! This time I'd like to give my wife #b#t4031043#s#k... They have a very pleasant scent, and I heard they're found deep in the forest... I heard the place where they exist doesn't let everyone in; only a selected few, I think. Something about a #p609# in #m10005000# and something something..."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Please get me #b20 #t4031043#s#k. I think 20 will cover the house with that pleasant scent. Please hurry!"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "I understand... my wife's birthday is coming up and I am screwed! Please come back if you have some spare time."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Ohhh... you got me #b20 #b#t4031043#s#k~! This is awesome... I can't believe you went deep into the forest and got these flowers... there's a story about this flower where it supposedly doesn't die for 500 years. With this, I can make the whole house smell like flowers."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh, and... since you have worked hard for me, I should reward you well. I found this glove in the ship. Some travelers leave things here and there. It looks like something you might need, so take it."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "If you have time, why not try going back into the forest? You might find an important item in there. I can't guarantee it since obviously I've never been there before, so please don't come back complaining if all you can find is trash."
        }
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirName": "stop",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "sub"
        },
        "item": {
          "_dirName": "item",
          "_dirType": "sub",
          "0": {
            "_dirName": "0",
            "_dirType": "String",
            "_value": "You haven't gotten the #b#t4031043#s#k yet. There's a #p609# in #m10005000# and I heard that with that you can go to the place where the #t4031043#s#k are. Please go into the forest and collect the #t4031043#s#k for me. I need 20 to make my wife's birthday present."
          }
        }
      }
    }
